---
title: Mumbai White Fish & Bengali Coconut Sauce with Honey-Roasted Veggies & Mixed Leaf Salad
description: A fresh cut of fish is so refreshing, but how about darkening the taste with some delicious Mumbai spice and a
coconutty Bengali sauce drizzzled on top? It won’t disappoint and might even become a new fish favourite!

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
